  "prompt": "Where can I get best quality Build In Wardrobes in Guildford?",
  "response": "Finding high-quality built-in wardrobes in Guildford can be easier if you consider the following options:\n\n1. **Local Furniture Stores**:\n   - **John Lewis & Partners**: They offer a range of bespoke furniture options, including built-in wardrobes.\n   - **Guildford Furniture Company**: Known for their handcrafted furniture, they can provide tailored wardrobe solutions.\n\n2. **Specialized Wardrobe and Storage Solutions**:\n   - **Sharps**: They specialize in fitted wardrobes and storage solutions. Sharps has a good reputation for quality and customer service.\n   - **Hammonds**: Another company known for customized furniture, including built-in wardrobes. They have a showroom where you can view their products.\n\n3. **Interior Design Firms**:\n   - **Chloe Roberts Interiors**: Local design firms may offer or suggest high-quality wardrobe services.\n   - **HomeSmiths**: They can help design and procure fitted wardrobes.\n\n4. **Online Retailers and Services**:\n   - **Houzz**: A platform where you can find local professionals and read reviews.\n   - **Checkatrade**: This site allows you to find and review local tradesmen who specialize in fitted furniture.\n\n5. **Carpentry and Joinery Specialists**:\n   - **Guildford Joinery**: They can create bespoke built-in wardrobes tailored to your needs.\n   - **Surrey Hills Carpentry**: Highly skilled carpenters who can design and build custom wardrobes.\n\nBe sure to check customer reviews, credentials, and previous work portfolios to ensure you are opting for the highest quality provider.",
